obile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3616170\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Apr 07, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104trc1665702640753.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/trc1665702640753.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/trc1665702640753.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"trc1665702640753\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Page Name and Tab Label Text\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Page Name</span> and <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tab Label Text</span> specify the ValRep list for the field, in which:\n </p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"trc1665702640753__li_d42086e1_d42087e1_d42088e1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Page Name</span> is the name of the contained form or form instance name to be assigned as a tab page. It corresponds to the <var class=\"keyword varname\">Value</var> in a ValRep item\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"trc1665702640753__li_d42089e1_d42090e1_d42091e1\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tab Label Text</span> is the text displayed on the tab at runtime, and corresponds to the <var class=\"keyword varname\">Representation</var>.\n </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"trc1665702640753__p_d106349e1_d106350e1_d106351e1\">The order in which pages are entered determines their location in the tab widget. For more information see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hdy1665702557196.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hdy1665702557196.html\" title=\"This property defines the possible values that the field accepts. The ValRep consists of a Uniface list of one or more items, in which each item consists of a value and optional representation.\">ValRep</a>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"trc1665702640753__p_d106352e1_d106353e1_d106354e1\">In the TabEx widget, the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tab Label Text</span> can include images and text in the representation. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ksc1665702629947.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ksc1665702629947.html\" title=\"For the drop-down list, list box, and drag-and-drop widgets, the Representation can also specify an image (file or glyph) in the Representation.\">Images in ValRep Lists</a>.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"trc1665702640753__section_kz5_p43_zwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1227423e107\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"trc1665702640753__ul_kvn_r43_zwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"trc1665702640753__li_d42092e1_d42093e1_d42094e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bzj1665702641924.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bzj1665702641924.html\" title=\"The utab widget enables users to navigate through a collection of contained forms by clicking a tab to display the form. Uniface provides a logical widget called Tab, which is mapped to utab.\">utab (Tab)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"trc1665702640753__li_d42095e1_d42096e1_d42097e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gyf1688451219719.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gyf1688451219719.html\" title=\"The utabex widget enables users to navigate through a collection of contained forms by clicking a tab to display the form. The utabex widget is highly customizable, allowing extensive control over the appearance and behavior of the tabs. Uniface provides a logical widget called TabEx, which is mapped to utabex.\">utabex (TabEx)</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616170\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616170\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Page Name and Tab Label Text Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Apr 07, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Page Name and Tab Label Text The Page Name and Tab Label Text specify the ValRep list for the field, in which: Page Name is the name of the contained form or form instance name to be assigned as a tab page. It corresponds to the Value in a ValRep item Tab Label Text is the text displayed on the tab at runtime, and corresponds to the Representation . The order in which pages are entered determines their location in the tab widget. For more information see ValRep In the TabEx widget, the Tab Label Text can include images and text in the representation. For more information, see Images in ValRep Lists . Applies To utab (Tab) utabex (TabEx) Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}